<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1307851-one-of-the-things-i-loved-about-this-book">One of the things I loved about this book was the cooking. Anyone know of other novels where Italian cooking is included?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1307851'><a id="like_count_community_question_1307851" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1307851?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">12 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F36097619-the-tuscan-child">like</a></span>

